      "updated": 1776673648236,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": ". Steps to model LLD of any Systems:-\n    -> Requiremt Clarification from specs priovided.\n    -> Identify all the Use cases(prioritize them)\n    -> Identify Domains from Use cases.\n    -> Establish all Invariants for each Domain.\n    -> Find Aggregates among domains.\n    -> Establish Relationships among Aggregates.\n    -> Define Service Layers.\n    -> Define Repository Layers\n    -> Define Controllers Layers.\n    ",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": ". Steps to model LLD of any Systems:-\n    -> Requiremt Clarification from specs priovided.\n    -> Identify all the Use cases(prioritize them)\n    -> Identify Domains from Use cases.\n    -> Establish all Invariants for each Domain.\n    -> Find Aggregates among domains.\n    -> Establish Relationships among Aggregates.\n    -> Define Service Layers.\n    -> Define Repository Layers\n    -> Define Controllers Layers.\n    ",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
